          I'm also a massive nerd in the other sense of the word, I'm a big fan
          of a ton of different things, everything from How to Train Your Dragon
          to She-Ra<span class="accent">*</span>, and if you let me, I'll
          probably spend hours geeking out to you about them.
          <div style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></div>
